  16,46,It strike them chvila they bol asleep they never escape
  16,47,it strike them chvila they fearfully expecting it Tvoj Lord je Compassionate Merciful
  16,48,they nie seen all things Have created GOD Ich shadows surround them vela vlavo v total submission do GOD a willingly
  16,49,Do GOD prostrates everything heavens everything on zem! -Kazdy creature -A so robi angels; maly arrogance
